{
  "stem": "15694.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was just telling you that my father scolded me, and he told me that if I succeed and the henchmen-- his henchmen-- and I would kill Hitler, and his henchmen would continue, it could be worse than before.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Germans, who were still euphoric because they, at that time, they were victorious everywhere.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you could read [INAUDIBLE], wherever you cared to look, [SPEAKING GERMAN], Germany seeks on all frontiers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] as I say, my father was against it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said in the game of-- life is like a game of chess.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You should have thought about the consequences.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I had-- all I was thinking about was that if Hitler is going to die, if I should be successful, then Mother and Sister would hopefully come back.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Of course, they didn't live anymore, but we didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the first thing we have to do is now prepare to flee.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we shall do that in the morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I should be able to gather some food for us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I had some contact with the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we shall be prepared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I said, maybe we should flee now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He said, no, hang on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now it was another hour or so I slept, and I saw engines.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "An engine in my dream, I saw shooting up high in the air where I blocked it, and immediately everybody stared at me, and I found myself in the fields and guard dogs after me.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I woke up in a sweat, and it was still too early for the workers to get up.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I got up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And again, I stole myself out of the camp towards the station.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I couldn't go very near.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
